category: Text
requires: cygwin libcld0
sdesc: "C++ library and Python bindings for detecting language from UTF8 text, extracted from the Chromium browser (licensing & readmes)"
ldesc: "This is a straight port from the CLD (Compact Language Detector)
library embedded in Google's Chromium browser. The library detects the
language from provided UTF8 text (plain text or HTML). It's implemented in
C++, with very basic Python bindings."
